<h1>PyHtmlEdit README</h1>

<p class="initial">PyHtmlEdit is a simple Python text editor optimized for the kinds of HTML formatting that I commonly do.</p>

<h2>Author</h2>

<ul>
<li>Author: Ryan McGreal</li>
<li>Email: <a href="mailto:ryan@quandyfactory.com">ryan@quandyfactory.com</a></li>
<li>Homepage: <a href="http://quandyfactory.com/projects/pyhtmledit">http://quandyfactory.com/projects/pyhtmledit</a></li>
<li>Repository: <a href="http://github.com/quandyfactory/PyHtmlEdit">http://github.com/quandyfactory/PyHtmlEdit</a></li>
</ul>

<p>PyHtmlEdit was assembled from stuff I found online and some functions I've written.</p>


